PrecisOrder making known that the Governor in Council, having considered the petition of the Telecommunications Workers Union, declines to rescind TELECOM DECISION CRTC 92-12 as rendered by the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission on June 12, 1992, concerning competition in the provision of long-distance voice telephone service.
Attachments
precis:
Order making known that the Governor in Council, having considered the
petition of the Telecommunications Workers Union, declines to rescind
TELECOM DECISION CRTC 92-12 as rendered by the Canadian Radio-television
and Telecommunications Commission on June 12, 1992, concerning competition
in the provision of long-distance voice telephone service.
